    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduction to the setuptools_rust Module</title>

      <para>
        The <application>setuptools_rust</application> module provides a plugin
        to setuptools allowing for the compilation of Python extensions in Rust.
      </para>

      &lfs130_checked;

