        <xref linkend="pytest"/>
      </para>

    </sect3>

    <sect3 role="installation">
      <title>Installation of setuptools_rust</title>

      <para>
        Build the module:
      </para>

&build-wheel;

      <para>
        Now, as the <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> user:
      </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>&install-wheel; setuptools_rust</userinput></screen>

      <para>
        To test the installation, issue:
        <command>pytest --doctest-modules setuptools_rust tests</command>. One
        warning will be present about an API deprecation.
      </para>

    </sect3>

